# Quivi Temporary Data Compression

Compressed `.codex_tmp/` into `.codex_tmp.zip` using standard ZIP compression.

The archive was verified by opening it through .NET's ZIP reader and counting entries before the expanded folder was removed.

Verification result:

```text
ZIP_ENTRIES=10217
```

The ZIP format was chosen because it is easy for coding agents and Windows PowerShell to inspect or extract quickly with `Expand-Archive`.
